  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in the tagine pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced shiitake mushrooms and cook until they are tender.",
    "Add the tadka spice mix, cumin powder, coriander powder, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
